      <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <h2 id="intro">1. Tizim haqida umumiy ma'lumot</h2>

      <p>
        <strong>Random Test Generator</strong> — maktab va o'quv markazlar uchun ishlab chiqilgan
        web ilova bo'lib, u orqali:
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Savollar bazasini yaratish va boshqarish mumkin</li>
        <li>Bir nechta fanning savollarini alohida saqlash mumkin</li>
        <li>Excel fayl orqali minglab savolni bir vaqtda yuklash mumkin</li>
        <li>Har bir o'quvchi uchun <strong>boshqacha variant</strong> avtomatik yaratiladi</li>
        <li>Javob variantlari (A, B, C, D) <strong>random tartibda</strong> aralashtiriladi</li>
        <li>Natijani <strong>Word</strong> yoki <strong>Excel</strong> formatda yuklab olish mumkin</li>
        <li>Javoblar kaliti avtomatik hisoblab, alohida faylda chiqariladi</li>
      </ul>

      <div class="info">
        <p class="font-semibold text-blue-800 m-0">Tizim qanday ishlaydi?</p>
        <p class="text-blue-700 m-0 mt-1">
          Admin savollarni bazaga kiritadi → Test yaratish sahifasida fan, variant soni va savol sonini
          tanlaydi → Tizim har bir variant uchun tasodifiy savollar tanlab, javoblarni aralashtiradi →
          Word/Excel fayllar yuklab olinadi → Fayllar chop etiladi va o'quvchilarga tarqatiladi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <h2 id="login">2. Tizimga kirish (Login)</h2>

      <h3>2.1 Brauzerda ochish</h3>
      <p>Brauzerda quyidagi manzilni oching:</p>
      <div class="screen">http://localhost:3000</div>
      <p>Sahifa avtomatik ravishda kirish sahifasiga yo'naltiradi.</p>

      <h3>2.2 Login ma'lumotlari</h3>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Maydon</th><th>Qiymat</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><strong>Login (username)</strong></td><td><code>admin</code></td></tr>
          <tr><td><strong>Parol (password)</strong></td><td><code>Admin123!</code></td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <div class="warn">
        <p class="font-semibold text-amber-800 m-0">Muhim!</p>
        <p class="text-amber-700 m-0 mt-1">
          Tizimni ishga tushirishdan oldin <code>.env</code> faylda
          <code>ADMIN_USERNAME</code> va <code>ADMIN_PASSWORD</code> ni o'zgartiring.
          Standart parolni ishlatish xavfsiz emas!
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3>2.3 Tizimdan chiqish</h3>
      <p>
        Sahifaning yuqori o'ng burchagida admin nomi yonidagi
        <strong>"Chiqish"</strong> tugmasini bosing. Session avtomatik o'chiriladi.
      </p>

      <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <h2 id="dashboard">3. Dashboard (Bosh sahifa)</h2>

      <p>Tizimga kirganingizdan so'ng <strong>Dashboard</strong> sahifasi ochiladi. Bu sahifada:</p>

      <h3>3.1 Statistika kartochkalar</h3>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Karta</th><th>Nimani ko'rsatadi</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Jami savollar</td><td>Bazadagi barcha savollar soni</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Fanlar</td><td>Yaratilgan fanlar soni</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Yaratilgan testlar</td><td>Shu paytgacha generatsiya qilingan testlar</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>3.2 Fanlar bo'yicha jadval</h3>
      <p>
        Har bir fan uchun progress bar ko'rsatiladi. Bu orqali qaysi fanda ko'p, qaysi fanda
        kam savol borligini tezda bilib olish mumkin.
      </p>

      <h3>3.3 So'nggi testlar</h3>
      <p>
        Oxirgi 5 ta yaratilgan test ro'yxati ko'rsatiladi. "Ko'rish" havolasi orqali
        testning natija sahifasiga o'tish mumkin.
      </p>

      <h3>3.4 Tezkor harakatlar</h3>
      <p>Pastki qismda uchta tugma mavjud:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Savol qo'shish</strong> — savollar sahifasiga o'tadi</li>
        <li><strong>Excel import</strong> — import sahifasiga o'tadi</li>
        <li><strong>Test yaratish</strong> — generator sahifasiga o'tadi</li>
      </ul>

      <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <h2 id="subjects">4. Fanlar boshqaruvi</h2>

      <p>
        Chap menuda <strong>"Fanlar"</strong> bo'limini tanlang.
        Bu sahifada mavjud fanlar jadvali ko'rsatiladi.
      </p>

      <h3>4.1 Yangi fan qo'shish</h3>
      <ol class="steps">
        <li class="step"><span>Yuqori o'ng burchakdagi <strong>"Fan qo'shish"</strong> (ko'k) tugmani bosing.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span>Ochiladigan modal oynada <strong>Fan nomi</strong>ni kiriting (majburiy).</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span><strong>Tavsif</strong>ni kiriting (ixtiyoriy).</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span><strong>"Saqlash"</strong> tugmasini bosing.</span></li>
      </ol>

      <div class="tip">
        <p class="font-semibold text-green-800 m-0">Maslahat</p>
        <p class="text-green-700 m-0 mt-1">
          Fan nomi aniq va qisqa bo'lishi kerak. Masalan: <code>Matematika</code>, <code>Fizika</code>,
          <code>Ingliz tili 9-sinf</code>. Bir xil nomli fan ikki marta yaratilmaydi.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3>4.2 Fanni tahrirlash</h3>
      <p>
        Jadvalda fanni topib, o'ng tarafdagi <strong>qalam</strong> (✏️) ikonkasini bosing.
        Modal oynada ma'lumotlarni o'zgartirib, <strong>"Saqlash"</strong> ni bosing.
      </p>

      <h3>4.3 Fanni o'chirish</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Qizil axlat</strong> (🗑) ikonkasini bosing. Tasdiqlash so'ralganda
        <strong>"OK"</strong> ni tanlang.
      </p>

      <div class="warn">
        <p class="font-semibold text-amber-800 m-0">Diqqat!</p>
        <p class="text-amber-700 m-0 mt-1">
          Agar fanda savollar mavjud bo'lsa, fan o'chirilmaydi.
          Avval shu fandagi barcha savollarni o'chirib, keyin fanni o'chiring.
        </p>
      </div>

      <h3>4.4 Jadval ustunlari</h3>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Ustun</th><th>Ma'nosi</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Fan nomi</td><td>Fanning nomi</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Tavsif</td><td>Qo'shimcha izoh</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Savollar <span class="inline-block bg-indigo-100 text-indigo-700 px-1.5 rounded">ko'k</span></td><td>Ushbu fandagi savollar soni</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Testlar <span class="inline-block bg-purple-100 text-purple-700 px-1.5 rounded">binafsha</span></td><td>Bu fan bo'yicha yaratilgan testlar soni</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <h2 id="questions">5. Savollar boshqaruvi</h2>

      <p>Chap menuda <strong>"Savollar"</strong> bo'limini tanlang.</p>

      <h3>5.1 Yangi savol qo'shish (qo'lda)</h3>
      <ol class="steps">
        <li class="step"><span><strong>"Qo'shish"</strong> (ko'k) tugmasini bosing.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span><strong>Fan</strong>ni ro'yxatdan tanlang.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span><strong>Qiyinlik</strong>ni tanlang: Oson / O'rta / Qiyin.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span><strong>Savol matni</strong>ni kiriting.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span>To'rtta javob variantini kiriting: <strong>A, B, C, D</strong>.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span>To'g'ri javobni radiobutton orqali tanlang.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span><strong>"Saqlash"</strong>ni bosing.</span></li>
      </ol>

      <h3>5.2 Savolni tahrirlash</h3>
      <p>
        Jadvalda savolni topib, <strong>qalam</strong> ikonkasini bosing.
        Barcha maydonlar modal oynada ko'rinadi — o'zgartiring va saqlang.
      </p>

      <h3>5.3 Savolni o'chirish</h3>
      <p>
        <strong>Axlat</strong> ikonkasini bosing va tasdiqlang.
        O'chirilgan savol test tarixidan ham o'chirilmaydi (tarixiy ma'lumot saqlanadi).
      </p>

      <h3>5.4 Qidiruv va filtr</h3>
      <p>Sahifa tepasidagi qidiruv paneli:</p>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Maydon</th><th>Funksiya</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Qidirish (matn)</td><td>Savol matni bo'yicha qidiradi</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Fan (dropdown)</td><td>Faqat tanlangan fanning savollarini ko'rsatadi</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Qiyinlik</td><td>Oson / O'rta / Qiyin bo'yicha filtr</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Tozalash</td><td>Barcha filtrlarni olib tashlaydi</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>5.5 Sahifalash (Pagination)</h3>
      <p>
        Bir sahifada <strong>15 ta</strong> savol ko'rsatiladi.
        Pastdagi "← Oldingi" va "Keyingi →" tugmalar orqali o'tish mumkin.
      </p>

      <h3>5.6 Jadval ustunlari</h3>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Ustun</th><th>Ma'nosi</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td>Savol</td><td>Savol matni (qisqartirilgan) + A, B variantlari ko'rinadi</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Fan</td><td>Qaysi fanga tegishli</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Javob <span class="inline-block bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-1.5 rounded font-bold">A</span></td><td>To'g'ri javob harfi (yashil doira)</td></tr>
          <tr><td>Qiyinlik</td><td>Ko'k=Oson, Sariq=O'rta, Qizil=Qiyin</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <!-- ═══════════════════════════════════════════════════════ -->
      <h2 id="import">6. Excel orqali ommaviy import</h2>

      <p>
        Ko'p savolni bir vaqtda yuklash uchun Excel import xususiyatidan foydalaning.
        Chap menuda <strong>"Excel Import"</strong> ni tanlang.
      </p>

      <h3>6.1 Excel fayl formati</h3>
      <p>Faylda quyidagi ustunlar bo'lishi shart:</p>
      <table>
        <thead><tr><th>Ustun nomi</th><th>Majburiy?</th><th>Tavsif</th><th>Misol</th></tr></thead>
        <tbody>
          <tr><td><code>Question</code></td><td>✅ Ha</td><td>Savol matni</td><td>Suvning formulasi?</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>A</code></td><td>✅ Ha</td><td>A javob varianti</td><td>H₂O</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>B</code></td><td>✅ Ha</td><td>B javob varianti</td><td>CO₂</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>C</code></td><td>✅ Ha</td><td>C javob varianti</td><td>NaCl</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>D</code></td><td>✅ Ha</td><td>D javob varianti</td><td>O₂</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>Correct</code></td><td>✅ Ha</td><td>To'g'ri javob: A, B, C yoki D</td><td>A</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>Subject</code></td><td>❌ Yo'q</td><td>Fan nomi (avtomatik yaratiladi)</td><td>Kimyo</td></tr>
          <tr><td><code>Difficulty</code></td><td>❌ Yo'q</td><td>easy / medium / hard</td><td>medium</td></tr>
        </tbody>
      </table>

      <h3>6.2 Namuna fayllar</h3>
      <p>Import sahifasida ikki tugma mavjud:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Bo'sh shablon</strong> — faqat sarlavhalar bilan bo'sh fayl (o'zingiz to'ldirasiz)</li>
        <li><strong>63 ta namuna savol</strong> — 7 fandan tayyor savollar bilan fayl (darhol import qilish mumkin)</li>
      </ul>

      <h3>6.3 Importni amalga oshirish</h3>
      <ol class="steps">
        <li class="step"><span>Standart fan tanlang (agar Excel da Subject ustuni bo'lmasa).</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span>Faylni "Fayl tanlash" tugmasi orqali tanlang <em>yoki</em> faylni maydon ustiga tashlang (drag & drop).</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span><strong>"Yuklash va Import Qilish"</strong> tugmasini bosing.</span></li>
        <li class="step"><span>Natija ko'rsatiladi: nechta qo'shildi, nechta o'tkazib yuborildi, xatolar.</span></li>
      </ol>

